description:
Dwarves have 2 days to build the most amazing dwarf fortress ever known to protect their shrine. Then the dragon comes and kills the weak. All dwarves killed become zombies who come back to kill all the other dwarves.

OldManWillakers has awaken from his longer slumber, put on his old man slippers, and started to fix his game again. A bunch of us MindCrackers got together to play some more Dwarves vs Zombies.
